The Bank England said forecast liquidity shortage around 300 mln stg market today .
Among main factor , Bank said bill maturing official hand treasury bill take-up would drain 483 mln stg system target banker ' balance rise note circulation would take 50 mln 100 mln stg respectively .
Partially offsetting , exchequer transaction would add around 355 mln stg , Bank added .
